## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources, which may not encompass the full spectrum of Christian theological perspectives. Additionally, the interpretation of Christian teachings can vary significantly among different denominations and theological traditions, which may not be fully represented in the selected sources. Further research involving a broader range of theological texts and expert interviews could provide a more comprehensive understanding.